---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "../components/seo/Breadcrumbs.astro";

const canonicalPath = "/booking-policy/";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Booking Policy | Happy Faces LA"
  description="Booking, travel, and event policy details for Happy Faces LA."
  canonicalPath={canonicalPath}
>
  <Breadcrumbs
    items={[
      { label: "Home", href: "/" },
      { label: "Booking Policy", href: canonicalPath },
    ]}
  />
  <section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Booking Policy</h1>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">
          Travel &amp; Service Area
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Serving Los Angeles and nearby areas. Share your event city or ZIP
          code for availability.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Face Painting Parties from $150. Travel may be included or added
          depending on event location, distance, traffic, parking, and total
          booking size. Final pricing is confirmed before booking, so there are
          no surprise travel charges on the event day.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Overtime</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Additional time may be available if the artist's schedule allows.
          Overtime must be requested and approved before the scheduled end time.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          If approved, overtime is added to the final balance based on the
          services being provided and the additional time requested.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">
          Weather &amp; Outdoor Events
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Outdoor events are welcome, but face painting, glitter tattoos, face
          gems, and balloon twisting require safe working conditions.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Client should provide a shaded, protected setup area away from direct
          sun, rain, strong wind, sprinklers, smoke, dust, and unsafe heat. If
          conditions are unsafe, services may need to move indoors, pause, or be
          adjusted for safety.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          For best results, indoor or covered setup is recommended.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">
          Parking &amp; Setup
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Client is responsible for providing safe, nearby parking or covering
          required parking fees.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Please plan for a clean setup area with enough space for the artist,
          supplies, and guests. Difficult parking, valet-only locations, gated
          access, stairs, or long walking distances may affect setup time and
          should be shared before booking.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
